.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, electrician
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola
1. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
2. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the electrician is the dutch##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | electrician | coach    |
| Nationality   | dutch       | egyptian |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Beverage         | sprite    | cola   |

