The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, subway
1. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person eating apricot##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |
| Food          | apricot    | pepper |
| Birthday   | june       | september  |
| Sport         | rowing     | rugby  |
| Transport     | skateboard | subway |

